article: 105+ Rizz Jokes, Puns, & One-Liners to Impress Everyone
intro: Looking for a rizz joke to make everyone laugh out loud? We’ve got you covered! “Rizz” (short for charisma), is a slang term that means you’re able to charm and attract people. While it’s mainly used in romantic situations, it can also be used to shake up a boring conversation. In this article, we’re providing the best rizz jokes for any occasion, whether you’re trying to flirt with your crush or make everyone giggle in the group chat.
